description: Java tools for working with NGS data in the BAM format. This package depends on 'r-base' because Picard requires R to run some of its metrics commands. The 'picard-slim' package offers an installation of Picard without the  'r-base' dependency.
name: picard
summary: Java tools for working with NGS data in the BAM format
